snippet.title: Invitation To Fear - Announcement Trailer (Co-Op Horror Game)
snippet.description:
Invitation To Fear on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1802330/INVITATION_To_FEAR

Invitation To Fear is a horror survival game for 1 to 4 players. After receiving one of the invitations, you will wake up in an unfamiliar place. Before long, you will realize that a terrifying creature is wandering around the building. Don't let "her" find you.

#trailer #gametrailers #games #gaming
